{"tid":220144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有人大大聲話亂倫合法化","createTime":"2017-04-27T17:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T00:32:43.000Z","uid":112452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3363e618b14a71be64cbaa2ba44b38475a4558f1","tid":220144,"uid":112452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:49:38.000Z","msg":"仲話出軌一樣，咁點解唔出軌都當犯法<br />\n<br />\n說到道德禁忌，已婚人士在承諾過只可有單一伴侣下出軌也可算一項，可是就算以今天的大眾標準看，要出軌者為此負上刑事責任也太荒謬了。這回筆者走點捷徑，不去討論「亂倫」的所謂對錯，即使退一步假設亂倫是「不好的」、「不該做的」、「不潔的」，但說到底都是感情事，沒有傷害社會利益，沒有直接傷害第三者利益，說要因此監禁亂倫者，只能說香港法例為傳統道德觀念服務得也太周到了。<br />\n<br />\nlink, 好長 可以唔睇 無乜重點<br />\n<a href=\"http://blablabla-media.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B1%E8%AD%98%E5%B0%87%E4%BA%82%E5%80%AB%E9%9D%9E%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E5%8C%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblablabla-media.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A9%25B2%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%25AD%2598%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25BA%2582%25E5%2580%25AB%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%258C%2596%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8J7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=5044cb01\" target=\"_blank\">http://blablabla-media.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B1%E8%AD%98%E5%B0%87%E4%BA%82%E5%80%AB%E9%9D%9E%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E5%8C%96/</a>"},{"pid":"8ed71f1662bc19afc068d10714d617141796cece","tid":220144,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:57:21.000Z","msg":"出軌有法律禁止？<br />\n<br />\n成果如何？ 人要出軌根本冇法律可以阻止到"},{"pid":"d0df3a6315416b564e4bc3df821acd3f1a26a1a8","tid":220144,"uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:27:01.000Z","msg":"同性戀合法化，近親戀也不是病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cf3d5246d7fae6b704dc87f02221eebf7f2fa2","tid":220144,"uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:28:07.000Z","msg"